Judith Gereg v. Administrator, Unemployment Compensation Act (3691)

Hull, Daly and Bieluch, Js.

Argued November 14 decision released December 3, 1985 *547Walter R. Keenan, for the appellant (plaintiff). Richard T. Sponzo, assistant attorney general, with whom, on the brief, were Joseph I. Lieberman, attorney general, and Robert E. Walsh, assistant attorney general, for the appellee (defendant). Per Curiam.
